What if you didn't get on this train?
All right?

60
00:02:50.796 --> 00:02:52.506
What if you got on the next one
instead? What if you.

61
00:02:52.590 --> 00:02:57.177
an incredibly beautiful. clever.
funny lawyer who is gonna save the world.

62
