your best friend is a murderer?

82
00:05:25.534 --> 00:05:27.828
I'm not a murderer. I'm an assassin.

83
00:05:27.911 --> 00:05:29.872
I kill bad people.

84
00:05:30.998 --> 00:05:32.791
Really awful.

85
00:05:32.875 --> 00:05:35.002
- terrible people.
- For money.

86
00:05:35.085 --> 00:05:37.212
Well. if I did it for free.
I'd be a serial killer.

87
00:05:39.006 --> 00:05:42.051
And besides. I may not
even be doing it for much longer.

88
