93
00:05:53.562 --> 00:05:56.690
They said I've been acting out
'cause I was turning 50.

94
00:05:56.774 --> 00:05:58.275
- You're not 50.
- Right? That's what I said.

95
00:05:58.358 --> 00:05:59.818
And even if I was turning 50.

96
00:05:59.902 --> 00:06:02.488
I'm still fucking good at my job.

97
00:06:12.998 --> 00:06:16.251
