169
00:10:05.731 --> 00:10:08.942
Yeah. No. I mean. I can... I can do it.

170
00:10:09.026 --> 00:10:12.612
Uh. zero. seven. seven. zero. zero.

171
00:10:12.696 --> 00:10:14.072
nine. zero. zero.

172
00:10:14.156 --> 00:10:16.283
four. zero. three.

173
00:10:16.366 --> 00:10:18.952
Great. Got it.

174
00:10:19.036 --> 00:10:22.372
Right. but now you call me
so I have your number.

175
00:10:24.833 --> 00:10:27.586
Yeah. Yeah. of course.

176
00:10:31.840 --> 00:10:34.384
Ah. got it.

177
00:10:34.468 --> 00:10:35.677
Bye. Sam.

178
00:10:39.765 --> 00:10:42.017
<i>In a surprising turn of events.</i>

179
00:10:42.100 --> 00:10:44.478
<i>MP David Claybourne was absent
from the vote today...</i>

180
00:10:44.561 --> 00:10:45.812
- Body.
<i>- On the Transport Bill</i>

181
00:10:45.896 --> 00:10:48.648
<i>- he campaigned so diligently for.</i>
- Shit. shit. shit. shit!

182
