203
00:12:00.345 --> 00:12:03.014
No. He wasn't. Uh. this is everybody.

204
00:12:03.098 --> 00:12:04.641
Oh. my God.

205
00:12:04.724 --> 00:12:09.020
If-if The Director finds out
that we've lost an MP. we are both fucked!

206
00:12:09.104 --> 00:12:12.899
And-and by "fucked." I mean "dead."

207
00:12:12.983 --> 00:12:14.443
Yeah. I understood.

208
00:12:14.526 --> 00:12:16.111
Thank you.

209
00:12:16.194 --> 00:12:18.697
Hey. wait. Where are you going?

210
00:12:18.780 --> 00:12:20.740
