224
00:12:58.612 --> 00:12:59.738
Calm down?

225
00:12:59.821 --> 00:13:03.283
They stole my 24 million.
but I should calm down?

226
00:13:04.576 --> 00:13:05.702
I'm fucking calm.

227
00:13:06.912 --> 00:13:10.874
And you?
You know what you're supposed to do?

228
00:13:10.957 --> 00:13:14.002
Yes. Dad. We got to find these women.
No one steals from you.

229
00:13:14.085 --> 00:13:15.420
Exactly.

230
00:13:16.922 --> 00:13:18.131
See?

231
00:13:19.216 --> 00:13:20.300
He gets it.

232
00:13:20.383 --> 00:13:24.679
So. why do I need you?

233
00:13:34.773 --> 00:13:37.275
Go find them.

234
00:13:39.819 --> 00:13:41.363
<i>Williams & Daughter.</i>

235
00:13:41.446 --> 00:13:43.406
Was there a tire jack
in the back of the car?

236
00:13:43.490 --> 00:13:45.116
Of course. We always pack one.

237
00:13:45.200 --> 00:13:47.577
Thank God for that.

238
00:13:47.661 --> 00:13:49.621
I thought I was going crazy.

239
00:13:49.704 --> 00:13:51.164
I think we're being followed.

240
00:13:51.248 --> 00:13:54.626
I don't know who it is. though.
I'll tell you who it's not.

241
00:13:54.709 --> 00:13:56.545
A kind German man
who's currently in the boot of your car.

242
00:13:56.628 --> 00:13:57.879
